      "description": "Looking for a reliable daily driver that won't break the bank? This vehicle is ready for its next chapter! While it shows some honest wear and tear from its years on the road, it remains a functional and dependable choice for anyone needing practical transportation. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that still has plenty of life left to give!",
