    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age. Mechanically, the engine and transmission are sound, but you may notice some minor fluid leaks and a suspension that feels a bit soft. The exterior has several small dings and some clear coat peeling on the roof, while the interior shows moderate wear on the driver's seat and carpet. It is a solid, functional car for someone who prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
