      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has clearly been well-maintained by its previous owners. The exterior still carries a great shine, though upon close inspection, you will notice some minor road rash on the front bumper and a few light surface scratches. The interior is clean and free of any major stains or tears, and all electronic components are in working order. It offers a smooth ride and is mechanically sound, making it a reliable and attractive option for anyone looking for a quality pre-owned car.",
      "price": 32500.0,
